PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue amending Part I (PRECIOUS METAL COINS) of the Schedule to the Royal Canadian Mint Act in order to make provision for the minting of a series of coins which would replicate the first domestically-produced coins struck in 1908 at the Ottawa Branch of England's Royal Mint.
